<plot>Jack, a widowed retiree, gambles daily at the run-down Lucky Star. When two young factory workers accost him, Magda, a grizzled gambler everyone believes to be crazy, comes to his defence and an awkward friendship blossoms between the two lonely souls. In the tawdry atmosphere of the Lucky Star, Big Money explores the nature of solitude, the longing for connection and the need to dream</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?069660</url></doc>
